graph TD
    User[用户操作] --> Mode{调用方式?}
    
    Mode -- loadAd --> Load1[发起请求]
    Load1 -- 失败 --> Fail1[回调 onAdFailed -> 结束]
    Load1 -- 成功 --> Success1[回调 onAdLoaded -> 等待]
    Success1 --> Show[用户调用 showAd]
    
    Mode -- loadAndShow --> Load2[发起请求]
    Load2 -- 失败 --> AutoFail[回调 onAdFailed]
    AutoFail -- autoRefresh=true --> Retry[启动计时器重试] --> Load2
    Load2 -- 成功 --> AutoSuccess[回调 onAdLoaded]
    AutoSuccess --> AutoShow[自动调用 showAd]
    
    Show --> StartTimer{autoRefresh=true?}
    AutoShow --> StartTimer
    
    StartTimer -- Yes --> Timer[启动计时器]
    StartTimer -- No --> DisplayOnly[仅展示不刷新]
    
    Timer -- 到期 --> LoopLoad[自动 loadAd]
    LoopLoad -- 成功 --> LoopShow[自动 showAd] --> Timer
    LoopLoad -- 失败 --> LoopFail[回调 onAdFailed]
    LoopFail -- autoRefresh=true --> RetryLoop[启动计时器重试] --> LoopLoad